           SHORT="A Python stemming library"

cat << EOF
This package provides 16 stemmer algorithms (15 + Poerter English
stemmer) generated from Snowball algorithms.
It includes following language algorithms:
    Danish
    Dutch
    English (Standard, Porter)
    Finnish
    French
    German
    Hungarian
    Italian
    Norwegian
    Portuguese
    Romanian
    Russian
    Spanish
    Swedish
    Turkish
EOF
